   ibConnRDOutDatagrams OBJECT-TYPE 
   SYNTAX               Counter64 
   MAX-ACCESS           read-only 
   STATUS               current 
   DESCRIPTION 
      "Total number of Reliable Datagrams sent from this entity." 
